body.name: Winkalon King Bed Frame with Headboard, Bed Frame with Charging Station, Metal Platform Bed Frame King Size No Box Spring Needed, Modern Wood Upholstered Headboard and Under Bed Storage.
features: Sturdy Bed Frame - The queen bed frame is extremely sturdy, all metal frame. It also nicely has a headboard as well as a baseboard. It's built with heavy well fram aids in the support and comfort of the mattress. The metal slats are welded together into boxes sections and that they have ancho screw points literally everywhere.

Easy to Assemble and Take Apart - The bed frame comes with all the pieces and a simple instruction guide. It takes only one hour for two adults to assemble. Simple directions, match the numbers with corresponding parts and use tools to assemble. Everything including an Allen wrench are in the box along with extra hardware parts just in case you lose some.

Great Weight Capacity - Holds heavy weight (800 lbs) and doesn't shift or squeak. The platform bed frame queen size feels sturdy for overweight people. The platform part of the bed is designed with 14 metal slats and 3 heavy bars, 9 heavy-duty steel support legs to withstand your wild kids! Doesn't squeek or wobble at once all the fasteners are snug when you turn around.

Great Storage under Bed - You also get that space under the bed that works as more room for storage. This bed frame queen size is high enough to put the small collapsible bins under for storage. It's enough space for a vacuum or broom to get underneath to clean which is a bonus!

Ergonomic Design - The queen bed frame with headboard comes with a padded component for comfortably resting your head on that straight headboard . The strong mental bed frame is very sturdy to keep your back perpendicular. The steel industrial look mixed with the MDF adds such a rich tone to the space.
Please Note - The CBBPET comes with a one-year warranty, so if you experience missing spare parts or bent bars, please contact us promptly.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 13, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Robust, well-designed bed frame built to last: Excellent Value!
reviews.reviewText: This well-designed, easy to assemble bed frame is made to last for years. We spent quite a long time searching for a queen-sized bed frame that wouldn't have the issues other inexpensive bed frames we've owned which usually is either center support failure or headboard/footboard separation. If you look at the listing, you will see this is made from robust square tube iron. This robustness carries through the entire design of this bed, from the center support to the bed slats; even the fasteners are heavy duty.Aesthetically, this leaves a little to be desired as it lends the piece a more industrial look but not obtrusively so. One does need to keep in mind that inexpensive furniture has to make sacrifices in some areas, in this case the mfr decided to give up a bit on aesthetics in favor of a robust, well-made bed frame.The added electrical and USB outlets is a very helpful feature that is recommended if you like to use your ipad or laptop in bed.The one area of criticism is that the frame itself could have been made 2 inches shorter and 1 inches less wide as a queen sized mattress is a bit smaller than the actual bed frame. If this frame had these dimension it would receive 5 stars. (btw, reducing the size of the frame would result not only in a better product but also in cost savings for the mfr. and shipper.
